trans-unit.source: Represents a content anchor or cargo resource for an <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Reprezentuje zawartości zakotwiczenia lub ładunku zasobu <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: AnnotationResource elements are used to model <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors%2A> (the data that is being annotated) and <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos%2A> (the data provided by the user such as a text note) in an <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation>.
trans-unit.target: Elementy AnnotationResource służą do modelu <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors%2A>(dane, które jest adnotacją) i <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos%2A>(dane dostarczone przez użytkownika, takie jak Uwaga tekst) w <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation>.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation> </xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors%2A>

trans-unit.source: Through the use of <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource.ContentLocators%2A> an AnnotationResource can refer to the content, directly contain the content, or both.
trans-unit.target: Za pośrednictwem <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource.ContentLocators%2A>AnnotationResource można odwoływać się do zawartości, bezpośrednio zawierać zawartość lub obie.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource.ContentLocators%2A>
